plot: As he puts a price on Shane's head, Vic is asked to prove his loyalty to Beltran by killing Pezuela.

Vic and Ronnie are using up every last method, illegal or otherwise available; to find Shane. Mackey assures Aceveda that he still the main player to to take down Beltran as Pezuela connection. Corinne makes decision about the last call with Mara. Meanwhile Aceveda has to prove himself to someone.—ANDUG8
